Mix refried beans with hot bean dip in a bowl; spread the bean mixture in an even layer over a pizza pan. Mix avocados with salsa in a bowl; spread mixture over the bean mixture. Place dollops of sour cream over avocado layer and spread into an even layer; top with shredded Cheddar cheese. Sprinkle black olives, diced tomatoes, and green onions over the dip. Chill at least 1 hour before serving.